txt.en: 'Oooh, look at them wriggling in there. Good work, [placeholder]. These will be delicious fried up with some butter.'
Crayfish traps can be found along the Anduin River in Duskenvale.\n\nYou should collect the crayfish traps.
Tassila can be found at the river docks in Arhaim.\n\nYou should bring the trout to Tassila.
Tassila, a fisherman in Arhaim, has asked for your help retrieving crayfish traps from along the river-bank.

'One other thing you can do for me, since you're offering, is to check the crayfish traps. Crayfishing is even easier than normal fishing. You just bait the traps, leave them for a couple days, and come back to see if anything crawled on in there. You can find the traps along the river-bank.'
